data.description: Beautiful and spacious ranch style home ready for new owners. All the major work has been done. Updated electrical panel and lighting, Newer windows throughout, new furnace and humidifier in 2020, Newer AC unit, and 6 ft. privacy fence. The roof is approx. 7 years old! All appliances are staying including the washer and dryer in this one! Hardwood floors throughout, Large living room with charming seat area surrounding the beautiful stone fireplace. Master suite equipped with private remodeled bathroom. Walk out basement with additional space on the patio. Large fully fenced backyard with 2 car garage and 2nd laundry hookups. Conveniently located near the local parks and close to the highways making for an easy commute to about anywhere in the metro area. Don't miss out on this great opportunity! Solar Panels purchased in 2020 can stay if the new buyers want to take over the payments or add the cost of system into price of the home. Sellers will have solar panels professionally removed.
